{"tid":2362113,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"水上悟志老師既作品真係好撚正","createTime":"2021-01-11T08:22:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-12T04:22:17.000Z","uid":205394,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0769b4f7b9212f081430625167b9f305a8d31dc0","tid":2362113,"uid":205394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T08:22:45.000Z","msg":"水上老師既作品都好撚正<br />\n不論長篇定短篇都好有feel<br />\n不過水上老師既作品真係好難推廣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為佢長篇作品骨架係少年向，但內容卻好青年向<br />\n佢表面係熱血戰鬥<br />\n但其實真正講既係青少年成長既過程<br />\n成個內容都極度慢熱<br />\n要睇晒大篇幅先會明白佢既精彩<br />\n佢每一個情感既爆發位都係有極長既鋪排<br />\n唔由頭睇到尾好難get到果一瞬間果一幕有幾感人<br />\n<br />\n例如，雨宮為左東雲而喊果段<br />\n佢無因為東雲死左而即刻爆seed打爆敵人，都無喊<br />\n一直都好淡淡咁憂傷<br />\n直到佢後黎知道東雲將願望用黎傳功比自己果下<br />\n真係諗返起都眼濕濕<br />\n同樣，真介因為灼岩變左舊石而黑化<br />\n一直口upup要復仇復仇<br />\n最後佢比佢把刀既虛擬人格開導<br />\n一刀劈開所有怨念<br />\n連讀者都感受到佢果種撥雲見日既爽快感<br />\n<br />\n佢表面上係戰鬥漫畫<br />\n但每個主角既實力成長都唔係因為佢修行左乜新招式<br />\n練左咩絕技<br />\n或者突然爆seed<br />\n水上老師總係好巧妙咁將主角既實力同佢既內心成長掛勾<br />\n主角每次實力既成長都同佢心理既成長同步<br />\n好似迅火抱怨點解自己從少比人丟去山度咁辛苦生活<br />\n但佢後黎終於面對自己內心，其實因為咁樣佢先可以咁強，識咁多朋友<br />\n<br />\n水上老師既作品真係好撚正<br />\n時不時都會拎返出黎讀下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最鍾意係真介<br />\n貫穿妖狐三部既角色<br />\n都係唯一一個無任何背景但成就非凡既人類角色<br />\n由農民出身變成一代宗師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後用一碗粥收左妖狐迅火皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3447006497cb898edd23415d9aea873c2d592a8","tid":2362113,"uid":42856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T08:24:32.000Z","msg":"可惜佢d新番跌灑watt<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d62b27328e5f43ccc60106bf46e9278a4fe367e2","tid":2362113,"uid":336782,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T09:15:03.000Z","msg":"魂環<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a61e43afb14d657401697a716f9f87c10a95a15","tid":2362113,"uid":230594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T09:51:32.000Z","msg":"可惜宜家養老Feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新作不定期連載"},{"pid":"7e463c2d24bb240b7390d724ff53b6c2b636cee9","tid":2362113,"uid":8017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a61e43afb14d657401697a716f9f87c10a95a15","tid":2362113,"uid":230594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T09:51:32.000Z","msg":"可惜宜家養老Feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新作不定期連載"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T11:00:16.000Z","msg":"想問新作係咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇完戰國妖狐同魂環就無睇"},{"pid":"3d13043d94d2e1b817cb5a8df41c0aece592c0a6","tid":2362113,"uid":230594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e463c2d24bb240b7390d724ff53b6c2b636cee9","tid":2362113,"uid":8017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a61e43afb14d657401697a716f9f87c10a95a15","tid":2362113,"uid":230594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T09:51:32.000Z","msg":"可惜宜家養老Feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新作不定期連載"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T11:00:16.000Z","msg":"想問新作係咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇完戰國妖狐同魂環就無睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T11:25:01.000Z","msg":"譯名好似係 終末的索魯特"},{"pid":"edddd16c0cce3b80c89c8b1084c557abe4bab591","tid":2362113,"uid":115270,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T00:49:37.000Z","msg":"剩係睇過魂環同planet with, <br />\n前者同當年第一次睇火之鳥一樣睇到嘩一聲，後者好普通 ..."},{"pid":"d86eacda24cb8bb6b288c4697ee00156bc2bb17b","tid":2362113,"uid":32221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T00:53:29.000Z","msg":"水上最大問題係畫風唔夠大路<br />\n同高分少女作者一樣靠故事食飯<br />\n好難可以普及"},{"pid":"99645079fa37791931b30b227672291100708542","tid":2362113,"uid":225100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T00:56:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ced12a305964481a10a99965c9e8ee40b3936af","tid":2362113,"uid":141869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"edddd16c0cce3b80c89c8b1084c557abe4bab591","tid":2362113,"uid":115270,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T00:49:37.000Z","msg":"剩係睇過魂環同planet with, <br />\n前者同當年第一次睇火之鳥一樣睇到嘩一聲，後者好普通 ..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T01:14:31.000Z","msg":"當年planet with動畫好期待,<br />\n睇完真係有啲失望"},{"pid":"ae7ed38574ef57536a89416fc14af7a967061d61","tid":2362113,"uid":205394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T01:38:56.000Z","msg":"Planet with我覺得幾好睇喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n始終佢係以動畫化為前提既創作<br />\n動畫又只比到13集佢<br />\n<br />\n所以水上老師既創作完全版焗限<br />\n<br />\n水上老師最擅長既係情感既鋪排<br />\n所以篇幅咁短，老師無發揮空間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過本身請水上老師原創同步動畫化<br />\n就係因為水上老師既作品太正但唔適合13集既動畫化<br />\n先搵佢做呢套野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"767ef4f35013c89334b956e9fd4129fc1b96b5bc","tid":2362113,"uid":105358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T04:22:17.000Z","msg":"只係睇過planet with，勁撚好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一季之內描寫充分又高潮迭起，加埋90年代動畫用色人設，唯一一次睇季番有呢種觀影體驗"}]}